OUR PROJECTS

Gharaunda

  • The scheme is designed to provide life long care for adults with disabilities with provision for vocational /pre vocational trainings.

Niramaya –Health insurance scheme

  • It is as affordable health insurance scheme for PwDs under National trust act upto 1 lakh on reimbursement basis only. All PwDs covered under Nationat trust act are eligible

Day care scheme

We take the admission from the age group of 6-14 year.

Physiotherapy

  • Special Child Care
  • Orthopaedic Injuries
  • Muscle Imbalance
  • Arthritis, Spinal Care
  • Elderly Care/Stroke
  • Neurological Disorders
  • Speech Therapy
  • Prkinson ’s,Sports Injury

Gyan prabha-educational support scheme

  • This is an educational support scheme to a person with disability to pursue higher education or skill development courses leading to employment or self employment.
  • There are three categories of courses that Gyan Prabha supports i.e 1)professional courses 2)graduation and post graduation courses 3)vocational courses.
